message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product. It's designed to enhance your daily life with its unique features and high-quality materials. Given its exceptional value, I propose a price of $150 for it. I believe this offers a fair deal considering its worth to me and the benefits it provides. Please let me know if this works for you or if you'd like to discuss further.
Thank you for your offer, Alice. I appreciate the value of your product. I would like to propose a counteroffer of $120 for the product. I hope this aligns better with my budget.
